Added support for the `invoke.yml` configuration file.
Updated `invoke tests` to clean up after itself to be able to run idempotently.
Changed the CI matrix to only test the latest stable version of Nautobot for normal PRs.
Disabled CI from running on branch push.
Added a CI workflow to be able to run tests on a branch manually.
Changed the tests to clone the nautobot devicetype-library instead of netbox.
Changed the clone directory of the devicetype-library to use a temporary directory when running in docker.
